Player mechanics
----------------
Self depleting health bar
standard three hit combo
natural movement speed - briskwalking or sprinting? 


box mechanics
--------------
initial opening can cause health loss



power ups/items
===============
Each power
*Fish dance - A fish weapon to increase damage 
  ->Large Fishy dance (level 2 attack)
  ->Flying Circus Fish dance (level 3 attack) - shoots fish projectiles.
*pimp-hand -Power up that increases points currency in tandem with the combo system (twice upgradable)
  ->"where's my money"! 
  ->Scrub-be-gone
*dust devil (base attack) - sends enemy reeling, chance of colliding for a combo bonus
  ->Tornado (level 2 attack) 
  ->hurricane (level 3 attack)
*The Wife Beater  - attack for half damage, then triple damage.
*Summon the THUN-DA!!! - a strike that sends lightening to the nearest enemies, then stuns others still (twice upgradable)
*Budhi-smacker - reduces the amount of health loss per-second
  ->Ensmitenment- + a speed boost to  attacks
  ->Slap-gri-la - once activated there is no health loss persecond for the duration of the power up
  ->All-mighty-smiter - complete invincibility for the duration of the power-up. 
  
 *End of it all - a slap so powerful it creates a black hole sucking all in the near vicinity into it.
  
 *1000 hand slap
 
 Upgrades
 Health upgrade
 pickup bar upgrade
 


